properties.title: Ampera Bridge at Night
properties.description: Stephanus Lie posted a photo: Captured from the top of Palembang Indah Mall, Ampera bridge has a straight position with Monumen Perjuangan Rakyat. I tried to turn this spot weakness to a meaningful composition. Everyone is invited to interpret this image personally.

properties.title: Palembang Colorful Night
properties.description: Stephanus Lie posted a photo: I took this image when I was on a business trip to Palembang. I had a promotional work with Palembang Indah Mall, one of largest malls at Palembang. After finishing my jobs there, I asked permission to capture the night life of Palembang from the top of the building. Access granted and... voila! I've got this beautiful scenery with glittering Ampera bridge as a sweet bonus... ^^

properties.title: Ampera Bridge
properties.description: Stephanus Lie posted a photo: I took this picture from "Benteng Kuto Besak", an old military fort at Musi riverside, Palembang. My native driver drove me there when I ask to have a sweet angle to shot Ampera Bridge, the famous landmark of the city. People there says that this bridge has better view at night, but I don't have time to enjoy that luxury in this business trip. So, this is it. Not bad, I think. I love the clean blue sky there, better than Jakarta's polluted grey one.
